Hey, what's the matter, Leo?

60
00:04:08,541 --> 00:04:11,541
You're so quiet. You got
anything interesting to say?

61
00:04:11,625 --> 00:04:12,500
Not really.

62
00:04:12,583 --> 00:04:14,000
Apparently.

63
00:04:14,083 --> 00:04:15,875
C'mon, big guy, speak up!

64
00:04:15,958 --> 00:04:18,416
You got any dirty jokes? Huh?

65
