Yggdrashiad Central Station.

255
00:12:31,333 --> 00:12:32,541
Yggdrashiad Central Station.

256
00:12:39,041 --> 00:12:39,958
[shouting]

257
00:12:41,583 --> 00:12:42,625
[crying]

258
