265
00:13:02,541 --> 00:13:03,833
And on this fine day,

266
00:13:03,916 --> 00:13:05,958
we stand in the heart
of Hellsalem's Lot.

267
00:13:06,041 --> 00:13:08,333
We're here at Yggdrashiad
Central Station,

268
00:13:08,416 --> 00:13:10,125
