269
00:13:10,208 --> 00:13:13,041
Utilizing this boy's
"All-seeing Eyes of the Gods",

270
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:14,833
we are about to conduct
a search of what is

271
00:13:14,916 --> 00:13:17,208
known as the
"Eternal Nothingness".

272
00:13:17,291 --> 00:13:19,625
This could likely be the
first time in human history

273
00:13:19,708 --> 00:13:22,708
that we're able to witness
the true forms of the Elder 13.

274
00:13:22,791 --> 00:13:24,208
Listen.

275
00:13:24,291 --> 00:13:27,208
Close your eyes the moment
that you feel you're in danger.

276
00:13:28,708 --> 00:13:29,791
No.

277
00:13:29,875 --> 00:13:31,375
