second, if possible.

279
00:13:34,208 --> 00:13:35,000
No.

280
00:13:35,083 --> 00:13:36,916
Wait till the last nanosecond,

281
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,708
and once you feel
all hope is lost

282
00:13:38,791 --> 00:13:40,333
and you're certain
to die a ghastly

283
00:13:40,416 --> 00:13:41,625
death and all you can think is

284
00:13:41,708 --> 00:13:45,000
"Stop, please, I can't
take any more!"

285
00:13:45,083 --> 00:13:47,083
Wait one second
longer, then close them.

286
00:13:47,166 --> 00:13:48,375
[ZAPP]
Enough, already.

287
00:13:53,666 --> 00:13:55,208
[ABRAMS]
"Noble beings shrouded

288
00:13:55,291 --> 00:13:57,125
with shimmering, scarlet wings."

289
00:13:57,208 --> 00:13:59,916
You do remember the color
of their aura, correct?

290
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:00,916
[LEO]
Yes.

291
00:14:02,166 --> 00:14:03,833
Let me know if you see one.

292
00:14:03,916 --> 00:14:05,708
Or if you see all 13 of them.

293
00:14:05,791 --> 00:14:08,166
Just as soon as we can confirm
that they're down there,

294
00:14:08,250 --> 00:14:09,916
we'll be done here.

295
00:14:33,958 --> 00:14:35,750
[ABRAMS]
Leo! Are you all right?

296
00:14:37,375 --> 00:14:38,625
What the hell did you see?

297
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:42,875
[LEO]
It's really bad.

298
00:14:44,833 --> 00:14:47,708
It's like a crimson
flood down there.

299
00:14:47,791 --> 00:14:50,166
There's a lot more
than 13 of them.

300
00:14:51,625 --> 00:14:53,083
The entire void.

301
00:14:53,166 --> 00:14:55,333
It's completely full of them.

302
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:58,916
[phone ringing]

303
00:15:00,166 --> 00:15:01,083
[KLAUS]
Go ahead.

304
00:15:01,166 --> 00:15:02,125
[GILBERT]
Young Sir,

305
00:15:02,208 --> 00:15:04,291
