317
00:15:40,083 --> 00:15:41,291
[HLPD OFFICER 2]
They wiped them out!

318
00:15:41,375 --> 00:15:42,500
[HLPD OFFICER 3]
Be careful!

319
00:15:42,583 --> 00:15:43,875
They become ghouls
when they attack!

320
00:15:43,958 --> 00:15:45,291
