325
00:15:51,541 --> 00:15:52,833
[STARPHASE]
Don't worry, we'll be fine.

326
00:15:52,916 --> 00:15:55,416
Send the specialists
for special jobs.

327
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:58,166
[KK] Ugh, this couldn't
be any more tragic.

328
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:00,916
Getting paired up with
this black-hearted schemer.

329
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,000
[STARPHASE] Try to look
on the bright side, K.K.

330
00:16:03,083 --> 00:16:04,416
This is a hell of
a lot better than

331
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:06,458
