the elders on your own.

332
00:16:06,541 --> 00:16:08,416
So, hey, you're welcome.

333
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:10,458
[KK]
I've been waiting for this

334
00:16:10,541 --> 00:16:11,791
for three years.

335
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:13,583
[STARPHASE]
You don't say.

336
00:16:13,666 --> 00:16:15,791
Me, personally, I've
spent all my time just

337
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:17,833
wishing this day
would never come.

338
00:16:17,916 --> 00:16:20,041
You're hopeless, you know that?

339
00:16:20,125 --> 00:16:21,958
I've got a proclivity
for peace and quiet.

340
00:16:24,166 --> 00:16:26,208
Nine, five, four.

341
00:16:26,291 --> 00:16:27,250
Blood Bullet Arts!

342
00:16:27,333 --> 00:16:29,458
Esmeralda. Blood Freeze style!

343
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:36,291
[KK]
Electrigger. 1.25. Gigawatt!

344
00:16:36,375 --> 00:16:38,375
[STARPHASE]
Espada del Cero. Absoluto!

345
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:44,625
[MAN]
Is that them?

346
00:16:44,708 --> 00:16:47,375
The friends you'd like to
see mercilessly slaughtered?

347
00:16:47,458 --> 00:16:48,833
[WOMAN]
Take caution now.

348
00:16:48,916 --> 00:16:50,833
There's a slim chance they
might be able to kill you.

349
00:16:50,916 --> 00:16:52,458
We hold them for four minutes.

350
00:16:52,541 --> 00:16:53,791
Don't tell me what to do.

351
00:16:56,416 --> 00:16:57,541
[STARPHASE]
You ready?

352
00:16:57,625 --> 00:16:58,833
[KK]
Always.

353
00:17:01,291 --> 00:17:02,791
[ZAPP] I know you're
just doing your job,

354
00:17:02,875 --> 00:17:05,375
but I need you to
do it a lot faster.

355
00:17:11,166 --> 00:17:12,875
[LEO]
So that's what they--

356
00:17:35,791 --> 00:17:37,000
[LEO]
The "Nothingness"

357
00:17:37,083 --> 00:17:38,250
is swarming with those things.

358
00:17:38,333 --> 00:17:41,250
How have we been
safe until now?

359
00:17:41,333 --> 00:17:44,916
It would take only one of
them to infiltrate our society,

360
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:47,083
and they could blend
right in with us.

361
00:17:47,166 --> 00:17:49,000
Just one of them...

362
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:55,333
could destroy our world.

363
00:17:55,416 --> 00:17:57,833
--[shouting]
--[groaning]

364
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,750
[KLAUS]
Listen, Leonardo,

365
00:18:02,833 --> 00:18:05,791
we're going to be counting on
your eyes in the days to come.

366
00:18:05,875 --> 00:18:08,125
You can recognize a Blood Breed.

367
00:18:10,291 --> 00:18:12,083
And their vulnerability!

368
00:18:24,541 --> 00:18:26,208
[BOY]
Well, this takes me back.

369
00:18:26,291 --> 00:18:27,958
Did he take that picture?

370
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:30,958
[GIRL]
Why?

371
00:18:31,041 --> 00:18:32,375
[BOY]
I knew those eyes of his

372
00:18:32,458 --> 00:18:33,541
were the real deal.

373
00:18:35,833 --> 00:18:38,125
[WOMAN] I was really
looking forward to this,

374
00:18:38,208 --> 00:18:40,125
but you two let me down.

375
00:18:40,208 --> 00:18:42,416
[STARPHASE] Well, at least
we hurt your feelings.

376
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:43,791
[WOMAN]
I'd heard that you were all

377
00:18:43,875 --> 00:18:46,250
some sort of anti-Blood
Breed human weapon.

378
00:18:46,333 --> 00:18:49,791
But you're not
quite there, are you?

379
00:18:49,875 --> 00:18:52,291
I will admit that it's
impressive how your blood

380
00:18:52,375 --> 00:18:55,083
continues to attack
on a cellular level.

381
00:18:55,166 --> 00:18:58,000
You would think that it would
be an effectively fatal method

382
00:18:58,083 --> 00:18:59,916
since we feed on blood,

383
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:02,625
but our bodies immediately
repair themselves.

384
00:19:02,708 --> 00:19:05,541
As you see, all better now.

385
00:19:07,916 --> 00:19:09,458
[STARPHASE]
Do you really think

386
00:19:09,541 --> 00:19:10,875
that matters, monstress?

387
00:19:10,958 --> 00:19:15,333
It doesn't matter if it
takes 1,000 years or 1,500.

388
00:19:15,416 --> 00:19:18,708
I promise you that
humanity will defeat you.

389
00:19:18,791 --> 00:19:21,500
The day will come when
we solve the paradox

390
00:19:21,583 --> 00:19:23,500
of killing the immortal.

391
00:19:23,583 --> 00:19:26,416
Just wait.

392
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:29,875
I'm sure you realize I'm only
buying some time here,

393
00:19:29,958 --> 00:19:33,666
but did you stop to think that
it could be time well spent?

394
00:19:33,750 --> 00:19:36,291
And maybe I've stalled you
enough for the one human

395
00:19:36,375 --> 00:19:39,416
with fangs that can rip
apart an Elder to arrive?

396
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:40,916
Think about that.

397
00:19:44,625 --> 00:19:47,458
[KLAUS] Brain Grid
Blood Battle Technique.

398
00:19:47,541 --> 00:19:48,666
