...Seal you.

403
00:20:05,916 --> 00:20:10,375
Despise me. Forgive me.
Resign yourself.

404
00:20:10,458 --> 00:20:14,625
I only commit such
brutality to protect mankind!

405
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:21,750
Form nine, nine, nine!
Ewiges Gefangnis!

406
00:20:34,041 --> 00:20:36,250
[LEO]
None of us were even capable

407
00:20:36,333 --> 00:20:38,458
