00:20:52,416 --> 00:20:57,083
Sure, we survived today,
but what happens tomorrow?

412
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:06,583
Oh, I see.

413
00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:09,166
I'd got it wrong.

414
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:11,750
Maybe there is hope for us.

415
00:21:11,833 --> 00:21:15,666
Maybe we can turn it around,
no matter how unlikely.

416
00:21:17,041 --> 00:21:20,333
But, I do know
one thing for certain.

417
00:21:20,416 --> 00:21:24,583
Getting your ass handed
to you and giving up,

418
00:21:24,666 --> 00:21:27,041
they're completely
different things.

419
00:21:37,458 --> 00:21:39,416
You get what I'm saying, right?

420
00:21:40,625 --> 00:21:42,708
You can see them too, can't you?

421
00:21:46,791 --> 00:21:48,958
Maybe I can.

422
00:21:49,041 --> 00:21:50,791
Are you--

423
00:21:50,875 --> 00:21:54,000
It's more fun if you
try to guess what I am.

